{"tid":1536714,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急) 停止大規模破壞港鐵!!!!","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:45:42.000Z","uid":191648,"like":15,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"36c6a5186d9aa528e222a6920c922d9e2284620e","tid":1536714,"uid":191648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:59:35.000Z","msg":"預左俾人屌 不過我屌曬你地先!! 破壞狗鐵係爽 但你一時嘅爽快可能累埋其他手足<br />\n<br />\n各位手足撤退個陣可唔可以正係破壞cctv保護番其他人就算 唔好連售票機、控制室都搞埋? 你地咁樣搞大佢只會俾班狗有理由好似831咁衝落月台、車廂拉人 打人 再者破壞完人、搭免費車仲要佢提供正常服務其實真係有少少狗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望各位現實少少先 要大部分人走到 暫時都仲係要靠狗鐵 尤其係冇車嘅學生 希望手足可以遲下先再清算狗鐵 <span style=\"color: gold;\">狗鐵都終有一日要還!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申: 不割 純粹提出意見"},{"pid":"4feaed0c43220abae84bcfe1c1789c628e952e6a","tid":1536714,"uid":191648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04422e79951d317bea58b4b2df44e2061d3ed88b","tid":1536714,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9e7508b03c49b8acaa2a0347374ccf28449f812","tid":1536714,"uid":224897,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"攪唔攪都可以落去打人，咪傻"},{"pid":"07e66176bec1d9c2ce6c8c13e381449400c81f4e","tid":1536714,"uid":33099,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"戇尻 無破壞佢一樣會停"},{"pid":"0c16c7fcd8eed4ba922ba0b713d14b2f5c60991f","tid":1536714,"uid":10434,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"都贊成既<br />\n有好多人見到都開始有微言<br />\n但理解前線咁做的"},{"pid":"ad3214aff22dea7ff1bd5c8458f64a83776419fd","tid":1536714,"uid":52839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"當初無搞過黨鐵 佢自己都封站黎運狗啦"},{"pid":"565c4fc1a0ecbc736453cb76619ffd25478b467d","tid":1536714,"uid":35667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"記唔記得上次機場<br />\n冇破壞全條東涌線停左"},{"pid":"6f118733a8a1ed9709458c7ded679fe7dec967b0","tid":1536714,"uid":129016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"唔搞就唔會落去？<br />\n<br />\n你番左兩個月前呀on9"},{"pid":"99d0bdc01bb38c331c2112252922322a3b61ba80","tid":1536714,"uid":282445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"撤退真係唔好再搭鐵喇<br />\n人地講到明班狗睇實晒cctv<br />\n你地仲搭咪俾人睇住黎食"},{"pid":"df9b540a13621e52544146ac617329a00199a96e","tid":1536714,"uid":189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:13.000Z","msg":"未遊行已經停幾個站，同破唔破壞冇關係，831停駛都係因為廢老打交先停，手足們好多都仲喺月台度，睇返